Taking care of this info can make it easier to qualify for funding and secure net-30, 60 and 90 trade credit terms. Join over 400,000 other small business owners who use Nav for instant access to:
  • Experian business credit score and report. This is the same report information small business lenders and insurers can use.

carouselApps.name: Support Schools
carouselApps.description:
The Support Schools app is free to download and costs your business nothing! 

Show your customer base that you support the community by fundraising for a local K–12 public school. All you need to do is choose a school and you can start accepting donations immediately! 

At the time of purchase, your employees simply ask customers to round up their purchases to help a local classroom. DonorsChoose, a top-rated charity, does the rest. All schools and classroom requests are vetted by staff and, once fundraising goals are met, DonorsChoose purchases the materials and distributes them to the school. 

The classroom will be notified of your business’s generous support and, in a few weeks, we’ll send you thank-you letters and photos from the very students you helped.
